      "id": "PopularPost216023",
      "post_content": "Useful creature types. The expansion right after Judgment (this card's expansion) was Onslaught, a block that was all about creature types. Look at [Aven Brigadier](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Aven Brigadier) for example, not to mention the scores of Soldier and Bird tribal effects as well, like [Seaside Haven](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Seaside Haven), [Catapult Master](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Catapult Master) or [Unified Strike](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Unified Strike). This card works well with all of them.",
